Python

Flask ‚Äì Web framework

TensorFlow / Keras

MobileNetV2 ‚Äì Image classification

HTML, CSS, JavaScript

JSON ‚Äì Mapping outfit recommendations


Installation & Setup
git clone https://github.com/lohita181/StyleFit.git
cd StyleFit
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py


Open in browser:

http://127.0.0.1:5000/